What if you own a Kenwood indash entertainment player that uses garmin as its navigation componenet.

Can that be upgraded also?

If you own a Kenwood DNX-7100 and it keeps rebooting on the start screen with this file, upgrade the GPS firmware to Version 2.90 from the Garmin website (it says it is for allowing the use of HDSD cards). Then it will work just fine.
